{"tid":2326374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"她酒醉摔車被送醫 急診室內喊「寶貝～」 醫師賞巴掌：公三小！","createTime":"2020-12-15T09:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T10:48:31.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"025d519663ab7000ec86ce2f032e37bda55dcfa8","tid":2326374,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"記者陳雕文／新北報導 <br />\n<br />\n新北市三峽區一名女子晚間喝醉還騎自行車，結果跌了個鼻青臉腫，民眾見狀協助報案送醫，院方詢問女子，「請問妳家屬的聯繫方式」，她便開始在急診室喊著「寶貝1～」、「寶貝2～」，醫師認為她藉酒裝瘋，怒賞一巴掌並罵，「公三小！」女子當場酒醒，事後委屈提告。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，林姓女子上個月29日晚間10點多，酒後騎自行車在民生街摔倒受傷，民眾協助報案，急診室的醫療人員看她身邊沒親屬陪同，因此說，「請問妳家屬的聯繫方式」，林女一臉疲憊回答，「寶貝1～」、「寶貝2～」接著被醫師賞了一巴掌。<br />\n<br />\n林女當場酒醒並解釋，「家人的聯絡電話，就是手機通訊錄裡的『寶貝1』與『寶貝2』啊！」事後林女越想越委屈，決定到派出所報案，並對賞巴掌的急診室醫師提出傷害告訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------<br />\n---<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201215/1876538.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20201215%2F1876538.htm&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=a448be33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201215/1876538.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b3ec1a26dfb438f52f88433bb871a410cb6b05b2","tid":2326374,"uid":10890,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"咁樣？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5cx1Xj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5cx1Xj.gif&h=8bfc6cbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef50da378982c7358d365c713e0cbf9baa846dda","tid":2326374,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:45:59.000Z","msg":"好機車惹"},{"pid":"a8c8a74fa92455fe6bade3bfc70a314ea65ce649","tid":2326374,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"都幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4d1152cd0e67fd1c414cc4cee0ced737533ae4","tid":2326374,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,